com.ardic.android.iotignite.interfaces

Interface IThing

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Thing

    public interface IThing
    Thing objects are way to use your IOT sensors&actuators with ARCLOUD. A Thing could be a real Sensor or anything act as an like sensor. For example Thing could be created which only generate random numbers and could done something with it. It's up to your imagination. To create & register Thing's the application has to be authenticated and the related Node must be registered before.
    Author:
    ARDIC
    See Also:
    Node, ThingListener, ThingType, ThingData, ThingDataType, ThingConfiguration, ThingManager
